title: Deadly Duo (1959) Craig Hill, Marcia Henderson, Robert Lowery

sources.title: Deadly Duo (1959) Craig Hill, Marcia Henderson, Robert Lowery
sources.description: Deadly Duo is a 1959 American film NOlR directed by Reginald Le Borg, starring Craig Hill, Marcia Henderson and Robert Lowery.   You can find out more about this movie from Wikipedia and there is also a review from the movie blog   ‘Noirish’ Noir Encyclopaedia .
